headline: You should consider these 3 stock picks, portfolio manager says
summary: Rockland Trust vice president and portfolio manager Michael Sayers joins Market Domination with Josh Lipton to share his top three stock picks: McCormick (MKC), TJX (TJX), and Copart (CPRT). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
